  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Claude Code just shipped a new release. Thirty-seven changes packed in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:60ecd19cb1d1acc296f8e92cd8a1c2929c3a50fdcff7f1733d08e1693d6a10da",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Auth and sessions dominate the diff. Seven new features.",
      "checksum": "sha256:896ddd837da0ea20e568df4324a460034bdb2f7e98d059d461834007d4fd6b93",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Twenty-five bug fixes. Seven improvements.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9caca6797bad954f049e87e7256b5a3301b820afe915d4f16c1f76e4f849522e",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 20
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Four of those fixes ship as a coordinated auth cluster.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2f553d28d270c86f565c31cf01ae8be55bc64fdc4e2d1c7251faf5a324669c37",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 25
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "One release. Four related breaks. All fixed together.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e4fb9097578e0587e4bdc7172b9f2b7fcc7ec06bb34f7c3de6defe5f970221a0",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 35
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Run claude project purge to wipe all your project transcripts, tasks, and file history in one command.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b7c0c530d1af5a23a8c4d69ea9d9e288c1ce9b08e64e0b3c773859c894848d33",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 6.408707482993197,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 43
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Use the dry run flag first. It lists exactly what gets deleted before anything is removed. You review the list, then decide.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0bac7fa9da05b64c3c24c3fb48a028d27f0390910620dd0e79a7b964133cbf56",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 8.266303854875284,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 60
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Nothing happens until you confirm. The dangerously skip permissions flag bypasses every permission prompt in Claude Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:46f9144bb8689d756186129bf6d53fbec62f0a97f5c8b42e613fe14ce0552d2b",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 7.012426303854875,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 82
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Writes to dot claude, dot git, dot vscode, and shell config files all go through without a pause.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bbb8c6e9523ca6d2ef4b86518581512e5736a0f7900b6ee1e6ddb732fb04aae0",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 5.804988662131519,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 99
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Built for CI pipelines and headless automation where any interruption breaks the flow.",
      "checksum": "sha256:41ee1164bff392b92159100011b2e8b10977fd307234d4ff1bd19ee248f5ea0d",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Zero prompts. Zero friction. OAuth now works directly in the terminal.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a4063db07f75986e8422215ee6832547e7ab24a81d4e78d8ced790a20905b786",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 130
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "If you are on WSL 2, SSH, or inside a devcontainer, the browser callback cannot reach localhost.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c10fe3799222b7a0dd22450a7e3e0f43a1d34212037fbc10399e45aa29d5e314",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 6.176507936507937,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 141
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Now you skip the redirect entirely. Paste the OAuth code at the terminal prompt and you are in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c00db29c35ae4f15ad400cfb89bb3302505f3f3566726c573fb474b5ac5e308b",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 5.061950113378685,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 158
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "No browser workarounds needed.\n\nAuth and session stability got a coordinated overhaul.",
      "checksum": "sha256:744c00fe390ec6cde7fd65bce30693afabf4a2ec40985f2c17964859284c3f4b",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 176
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Login state now survives reconnects. Token refresh no longer races on startup.",
      "checksum": "sha256:468439ad9c777a89feb2ca1949013d740878f87be429adb0a30f1752d50d4b28",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 188
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Session IDs persist correctly through update cycles.",
      "checksum": "sha256:15465817b19c808307999b07a2dcebe6707431f563fbd8f46ea2768fcf0e4b0b",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 200
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Run claude update to pull every one of these fixes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c91a46105146a255952809049ae432f26ef8dcf7942a4b065f698165aa193ca2",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 207
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "The auth cluster alone might be what you have been waiting for.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7a7b14163e5fed5963fede383b41cfcaf40a3e3a89f0bd4b1d20ee893110cd4f",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 217
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Drop a comment below with which one you actually needed most.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2901d443d3b328e55f4657ae2776634a0e2c5eae5d8f8fc9c1834bbbc314f628",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 229
    }
  ]
